{"tid":2245021,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"葉劉淑儀：境外投票先照顧內地城市符一國原則","createTime":"2020-10-16T01:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T10:55:27.000Z","uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"13452af1d812b1befbc3fba5c912adcfc3b61313","tid":2245021,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T01:56:55.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥早前表示，研究讓選民在內地可投票，認為是社會的訴求。行政會議成員、新民黨葉劉淑儀在本台節目表示，要推行境外投票必須修例，政府應提出修例建議，並先集中較多港人居住的內地城市，除了廣東省，亦應兼顧上海和北京等。<br />\n<br />\n被問到應否適用歐美等地，葉劉淑儀認為要按部就班，基於「一國」原則，應該先照顧內地城市，方便當地港人投票，有相關經驗後再推廣。 至於目前選舉相關法例列明，選民要「通常居住香港」，葉劉淑儀指法例沒明文定義，但參考英國的案例和裁決，若因學業或做生意原因到內地，符合法例規定。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2361827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2361827&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU7HKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=fb2d5b83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2361827</a>"},{"pid":"60d9a6d92ddc62025c952b9a45d41b0473bf44ab","tid":2245021,"uid":13745,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T01:58:02.000Z","msg":"爭取大陸有得投票=建設民主中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ebb738bea6b3181231290cc92eff40286c7f4b","tid":2245021,"uid":362865,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T01:58:36.000Z","msg":"我中文U，佢指香港國？"},{"pid":"98ff2a56b85ee8887116cb4bbcc9f1209ede0139","tid":2245021,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T01:59:32.000Z","msg":"一國就應該學祖國咁選人大代表啦，選乜撚垃圾會呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1086607/org/cb41bf012cd14c8ae4e5003e8bc70fda.jpg/ssb6vkHHunNebnsP6LvAeKQBg5Nj3PFTDnEfAQ5xHwE?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1086607%2Forg%2Fcb41bf012cd14c8ae4e5003e8bc70fda.jpg%2Fssb6vkHHunNebnsP6LvAeKQBg5Nj3PFTDnEfA